  <brief_title>Detection of Plasma DNA in Non Small Cell and Small Cell Lung Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Detection of Plasma DNA by Allelotyping in Non Small Cell and Small Cell Lung Cancer Patients. Evolution During Treatment and Follow-up.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
